  "text": "Earlier studies in our laboratory have demonstrated the oncogenic transformation potential of u.v.-irradiated standard EHV-1 in cultures of primary hamster embryo (HE) cells [CITATION_1] . In later work, infection of HE cells with non-irradiated, purified virus enriched for low-passage EHV-1 DI particles was shown to result in the simultaneous occurrence of oncogenic transformation and persistent infection [CITATION_2] . Careful examination of the virus produced by these persistently infected hamster cells revealed the production of standard EHV-1 exclusively.",
